MING WAN JAU SUEN KUK JIT LEI KEI
MING WAN JAU SUEN HUNG HAAK JEUK NEI JO YAN MOOT CHUI MEI
BIT LAU LUI, SAM SUEN, GANG BAT YING SE HEI
NGOH YUEN NANG, YAT SANG WING YUEN POOI BOON NEI

